data.description: This charming Cape Cod style home is a true gem, nestled in a prime location just 5 minutes away from Nationwide Children's Hospital and Capital University. Boasting a cozy, inviting atmosphere with classic architectural details, this property offers both comfort and convenience. Don't miss the chance to make this house your home--it's a rare find that's sure to capture your heart!
